{"lang":"zh","stage":3,"title":"short, easy phrases","sentences":[{"t":"看看时间。","en":"Look at the time.","r":"Kànkan shíjiān.","a":"n_636590fec0ad.mp3"},{"t":"我觉得是。","en":"I think so.","r":"Wǒ juéde shì.","a":"n_6b471b1e6913.mp3"},{"t":"今天我很开心。","en":"Today I'm happy.","r":"Jīntiān wǒ hěn kāixīn.","a":"n_8e2037119a57.mp3"},{"t":"她很开心。","en":"She's happy.","r":"Tā hěn kāixīn.","a":"n_29c39aa3a30d.mp3"},{"t":"我没钱。","en":"I don't have any money.","r":"Wǒ méi qián.","a":"n_e23d432abd20.mp3"},{"t":"你得睡觉了。","en":"You've got to sleep.","r":"Nǐ děi shuìjiào le.","a":"n_e9466d8e3f70.mp3"},{"t":"你去哪儿？","en":"Where are you going?","r":"Nǐ qù nǎr?","a":"n_fd84d80e4243.mp3"},{"t":"我昨天做了好多事。","en":"I did a lot yesterday.","r":"Wǒ zuótiān zuò le hǎoduō shì.","a":"n_8b43eaedf2bb.mp3"},{"t":"饭是我做的。","en":"I made the food.","r":"Fàn shì wǒ zuò de.","a":"n_984bae2b5cdf.mp3"},{"t":"我那时在家。","en":"I was at home.","r":"Wǒ nàshí zài jiā.","a":"n_79fe1fd63026.mp3"},{"t":"我那时特别累。","en":"I was very tired.","r":"Wǒ nàshí tèbié lèi.","a":"n_4bc5d1f1e4e7.mp3"},{"t":"我需要看医生。","en":"I need a doctor.","r":"Wǒ xūyào kàn yīshēng.","a":"n_27759d688d2a.mp3"},{"t":"你在家吗？","en":"Are you home?","r":"Nǐ zài jiā ma?","a":"n_b6011770494b.mp3"},{"t":"天气不好。","en":"The weather is bad.","r":"Tiānqì bù hǎo.","a":"n_3d827fc6f393.mp3"},{"t":"我感觉不舒服。","en":"I feel bad.","r":"Wǒ gǎnjué bù shūfu.","a":"n_1e089dc765de.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都看不见。","en":"I can't see anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu kàn bu jiàn.","a":"n_92ea897fa30c.mp3"},{"t":"我起得很早。","en":"I get up early.","r":"Wǒ qǐ de hěn zǎo.","a":"n_e5497cffff9f.mp3"},{"t":"这是安娜。","en":"This is Ana.","r":"Zhè shì Ānnà.","a":"n_c023a0cb23e5.mp3"},{"t":"我还没准备好。","en":"I'm not ready.","r":"Wǒ hái méi zhǔnbèi hǎo.","a":"n_9b5b878d4cb4.mp3"},{"t":"我想买两个。","en":"I want to buy two.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi liǎng gè.","a":"n_8768150feba6.mp3"},{"t":"我想买水。","en":"I want to buy water.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng mǎi shuǐ.","a":"n_a94258c9c3e1.mp3"},{"t":"你应该多睡点。","en":"You should sleep more.","r":"Nǐ yīnggāi duō shuì diǎn.","a":"n_a18f40e7a676.mp3"},{"t":"不远。","en":"It's not far.","r":"Bù yuǎn.","a":"n_de12ea54534e.mp3"},{"t":"我们坐火车去。","en":"We're going by train.","r":"Wǒmen zuò huǒchē qù.","a":"n_33375b924fbd.mp3"},{"t":"那个很便宜。","en":"That's cheap.","r":"Nàge hěn piányi.","a":"n_b047a853f2ab.mp3"},{"t":"这是卡洛斯。","en":"This is Carlos.","r":"Zhè shì Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_543d62085f2f.mp3"},{"t":"还早呢。","en":"It's still early.","r":"Hái zǎo ne.","a":"n_1183fe384835.mp3"},{"t":"你怎么了？","en":"What's wrong with you?","r":"Nǐ zěnme le?","a":"n_d5b4ba7ec89d.mp3"},{"t":"他怎么了？","en":"What's wrong with him?","r":"Tā zěnme le?","a":"n_35e7d3b7ee3d.mp3"},{"t":"你知道怎么回事吗？","en":"Do you know what's going on?","r":"Nǐ zhīdào zěnme huí shì ma?","a":"n_8b6c2b7b7868.mp3"},{"t":"我超爱睡觉。","en":"I love sleeping.","r":"Wǒ chāo ài shuìjiào.","a":"n_c37663799436.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道什么时候。","en":"I don't know when.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào shénme shíhou.","a":"n_18709eaeca9d.mp3"},{"t":"我整理床铺。","en":"I make my bed.","r":"Wǒ zhěnglǐ chuángpù.","a":"n_d616d95331be.mp3"},{"t":"我很晚才睡。","en":"I go to bed late.","r":"Wǒ hěn wǎn cái shuì.","a":"n_5732bae34139.mp3"},{"t":"我去市中心。","en":"I'm going downtown.","r":"Wǒ qù shìzhōngxīn.","a":"n_655a11cc0085.mp3"},{"t":"太贵了。","en":"It's very expensive.","r":"Tài guì le.","a":"n_fc76bcab9d59.mp3"},{"t":"今天我很难过。","en":"Today I'm sad.","r":"Jīntiān wǒ hěn nánguò.","a":"n_34270821e8e0.mp3"},{"t":"他很难过。","en":"He's sad.","r":"Tā hěn nánguò.","a":"n_9ddf94d184f8.mp3"},{"t":"今天很热。","en":"It's hot today.","r":"Jīntiān hěn rè.","a":"n_419a15073a26.mp3"},{"t":"我能做到。","en":"I can do it.","r":"Wǒ néng zuòdào.","a":"n_261140e224ce.mp3"},{"t":"你能做到吗？","en":"Can you do it?","r":"Nǐ néng zuòdào ma?","a":"n_3542fe607022.mp3"},{"t":"我问了个问题。","en":"I asked a question.","r":"Wǒ wèn le ge wèntí.","a":"n_134e57862565.mp3"},{"t":"你什么意思？","en":"What do you mean?","r":"Nǐ shénme yìsi?","a":"n_db1d7c96338e.mp3"},{"t":"我明天可以付钱。","en":"I can pay tomorrow.","r":"Wǒ míngtiān kěyǐ fùqián.","a":"n_a7ecb1821f4e.mp3"},{"t":"你坐出租车去吗？","en":"Are you going by taxi?","r":"Nǐ zuò chūzūchē qù ma?","a":"n_b554c4a5a9e2.mp3"},{"t":"我叫安娜。","en":"My name is Ana.","r":"Wǒ jiào Ānnà.","a":"n_3bba2f11d24e.mp3"},{"t":"他叫什么名字？","en":"What's his name?","r":"Tā jiào shénme míngzi?","a":"n_42ecc8ba164b.mp3"},{"t":"他叫卡洛斯。","en":"His name is Carlos.","r":"Tā jiào Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_050390335488.mp3"},{"t":"我有一只狗。","en":"I have a dog.","r":"Wǒ yǒu yì zhī gǒu.","a":"n_ed822c9dbeaf.mp3"},{"t":"你有空吗？","en":"Do you have a minute?","r":"Nǐ yǒu kòng ma?","a":"n_c9477c688779.mp3"},{"t":"今天是星期一。","en":"Today is Monday.","r":"Jīntiān shì xīngqīyī.","a":"n_4fc82216b233.mp3"},{"t":"我住在这儿。","en":"I live here.","r":"Wǒ zhù zài zhèr.","a":"n_b147a3da66d4.mp3"},{"t":"你病得不轻。","en":"You're really sick.","r":"Nǐ bìng de bù qīng.","a":"n_dacb3f21f305.mp3"},{"t":"大家都在哪儿？","en":"Where is everybody?","r":"Dàjiā dōu zài nǎr?","a":"n_8d0607fcc366.mp3"},{"t":"你得休息。","en":"You have to rest.","r":"Nǐ děi xiūxi.","a":"n_3ac3df7afe50.mp3"},{"t":"他不会等人。","en":"He doesn't know how to wait.","r":"Tā bú huì děng rén.","a":"n_d7ff74df59f3.mp3"},{"t":"我们得等一下。","en":"We need to wait.","r":"Wǒmen děi děng yíxià.","a":"n_15a738766702.mp3"},{"t":"到时候再说。","en":"We'll see.","r":"Dào shíhou zài shuō.","a":"n_4fe3a4bfd8c4.mp3"},{"t":"你今天能来吗？","en":"Can you come today?","r":"Nǐ jīntiān néng lái ma?","a":"n_162ddd5738c4.mp3"},{"t":"我刚下班。","en":"I'm coming from work.","r":"Wǒ gāng xiàbān.","a":"n_7ffb228c3dd6.mp3"},{"t":"你想喝点什么吗？","en":"Do you want to drink something?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng hē diǎn shénme ma?","a":"n_1a2c86aa8e5c.mp3"},{"t":"都是我付钱。","en":"I always pay.","r":"Dōu shì wǒ fùqián.","a":"n_2bcf60e84513.mp3"},{"t":"我待会儿付给你。","en":"I'll pay you later.","r":"Wǒ dāihuìr fù gěi nǐ.","a":"n_ef6d36b7bc23.mp3"},{"t":"那时候很小。","en":"It was very small.","r":"Nàshíhou hěn xiǎo.","a":"n_70733f2957dc.mp3"},{"t":"他是墨西哥人。","en":"He's from Mexico.","r":"Tā shì Mòxīgē rén.","a":"n_296e38d36883.mp3"},{"t":"天气真好。","en":"It's a nice day.","r":"Tiānqì zhēn hǎo.","a":"n_c8a45fdb7f15.mp3"},{"t":"我更想喝茶。","en":"I prefer tea.","r":"Wǒ gèng xiǎng hē chá.","a":"n_6af1d39b2aad.mp3"},{"t":"我能待在这儿吗？","en":"Can I stay here?","r":"Wǒ néng dāi zài zhèr ma?","a":"n_b00bb5dc557e.mp3"},{"t":"你知道这个地方吗？","en":"Do you know this place?","r":"Nǐ zhīdào zhège dìfang ma?","a":"n_3969b4b67b64.mp3"},{"t":"我熟悉这个城市。","en":"I know this city.","r":"Wǒ shúxī zhège chéngshì.","a":"n_2d7052416ab5.mp3"},{"t":"你今天干嘛？","en":"What are you doing today?","r":"Nǐ jīntiān gàn ma?","a":"n_66182c6eeb7e.mp3"},{"t":"你在哪儿说的？","en":"Where did you say it?","r":"Nǐ zài nǎr shuō de?","a":"n_f901158bddd6.mp3"},{"t":"真的很好吃。","en":"It's really good.","r":"Zhēn de hěn hǎochī.","a":"n_191fd102999a.mp3"},{"t":"我找到你的手机了。","en":"I found your phone.","r":"Wǒ zhǎodào nǐ de shǒujī le.","a":"n_0d2ed8825b17.mp3"},{"t":"我洗澡很快。","en":"I shower fast.","r":"Wǒ xǐzǎo hěn kuài.","a":"n_d24059236fa3.mp3"},{"t":"要十欧元。","en":"It costs ten euros.","r":"Yào shí ōuyuán.","a":"n_79168b0b3bdb.mp3"},{"t":"我昨天吃太多了。","en":"I ate a lot yesterday.","r":"Wǒ zuótiān chī tài duō le.","a":"n_17a0dac8fc29.mp3"},{"t":"他是个好人。","en":"He was a good person.","r":"Tā shì ge hǎorén.","a":"n_0c798d550304.mp3"},{"t":"我们明天做行吗？","en":"Can we do it tomorrow?","r":"Wǒmen míngtiān zuò xíng ma?","a":"n_7e9e5a20f323.mp3"},{"t":"我们可以之后再聊。","en":"We can talk afterward.","r":"Wǒmen kěyǐ zhīhòu zài liáo.","a":"n_f9624cc9a094.mp3"},{"t":"我们今天做点什么吧？","en":"Should we do something today?","r":"Wǒmen jīntiān zuò diǎn shénme ba?","a":"n_dc89b2899fab.mp3"},{"t":"我们办个派对吧？","en":"Should we throw a party?","r":"Wǒmen bàn ge pàiduì ba?","a":"n_5ca614b899e6.mp3"},{"t":"我们一起健身。","en":"We work out together.","r":"Wǒmen yìqǐ jiànshēn.","a":"n_00825a491d31.mp3"},{"t":"我做很多运动。","en":"I do a lot of sports.","r":"Wǒ zuò hěn duō yùndòng.","a":"n_e3fee2117b42.mp3"},{"t":"跟我说说怎么样。","en":"Tell me how it went.","r":"Gēn wǒ shuōshuo zěnmeyàng.","a":"n_6aa72e6f7cd2.mp3"},{"t":"你看那只狗。","en":"Look at that dog.","r":"Nǐ kàn nà zhī gǒu.","a":"n_4812aa37de2d.mp3"},{"t":"我不想起床。","en":"I don't want to get up.","r":"Wǒ bù xiǎng qǐchuáng.","a":"n_8bd91a521243.mp3"},{"t":"你想试试这个吗？","en":"Do you want to try this?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng shìshi zhège ma?","a":"n_214b61587460.mp3"},{"t":"现在两点了。","en":"It's two o'clock.","r":"Xiànzài liǎng diǎn le.","a":"n_1779d3d0c100.mp3"},{"t":"你叫什么名字？","en":"What's your name?","r":"Nǐ jiào shénme míngzi?","a":"n_dcdedf4368a8.mp3"},{"t":"你想跟我一起来吗？","en":"Do you want to come with me?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng gēn wǒ yìqǐ lái ma?","a":"n_5ae977c14cfe.mp3"},{"t":"我真的好渴。","en":"I'm really thirsty.","r":"Wǒ zhēn de hǎo kě.","a":"n_2f559e699e7e.mp3"},{"t":"你多大了？","en":"How old are you?","r":"Nǐ duō dà le?","a":"n_ff1749b232c0.mp3"},{"t":"我去打个电话。","en":"I'm going to call.","r":"Wǒ qù dǎ ge diànhuà.","a":"n_4d03d868104f.mp3"}]}